      "data": "ਅਬ ਕਹੁ ਰਾਮ; ਭਰੋਸਾ ਤੋਰਾ ॥",
      "page": 328,
      "line": 1
    },
    {
      "asset": "sbms",
      "type": "translation",
      "language": "en",
      "data": "Say now that my trust is in Thee, O Lord,"
    },
    {
      "asset": "sbms",
      "type": "translation",
      "language": "pa",
      "data": "ਦੱਸੋ! ਹੁਣ ਜਦ ਮੇਰਾ ਯਕੀਨ ਤੇਰੇ ਉਤੇ ਹੀ ਹੈ, ਹੇ ਸਾਹਿਬ!"
    },
    {
      "asset": "dssk",
      "type": "translation",
      "language": "en",
      "data": "If I say now that my trust is in You alone, Lord,"
    },
    {
      "asset": "nkft",
      "type": "translation",
      "language": "pa",
      "data": "ਹੇ ਭਾਈ! ਅਬ ਕਹੁ ਜੇ ਰਾਮ ਵਿਖੇ ਤੇਰਾ ਭਰੋਸਾ ਹੋ ਜਾਵੇ॥"
    },
    {
      "asset": "psst",
      "type": "translation",
      "language": "pa",
      "data": "(ਹੇ ਕਬੀਰ! ਪ੍ਰਭੂ ਦੀ ਹਜ਼ੂਰੀ ਵਿਚ) ਹੁਣ ਆਖ-ਹੇ ਪ੍ਰਭੂ! ਜਿਸ ਮਨੁੱਖ ਨੂੰ ਇਕ ਤੇਰਾ ਆਸਰਾ ਹੈ,"
    },
    {
      "asset": "snst",
      "type": "translation",
      "language": "es",
      "data": "Si uno dice, oh Señor, yo me apoyo sólo en Ti,"
    }
  ]
